Dynamic Host onfiguaration Protocol: Dynamically allocates Ip addresses
-------------------------------------
  1) Apllication layer protocol,used to provide
                                                Subnet Mask 
                                                Router Address 
                                                DNS Address  
                                                Vendor Class Identifier 
  2)DHCP is based on a client-server model and based on discovery, offer, request, and ACK.(DORA)messages
  
  3)DHCP port number for server is 67 and for the client is 68. 
    It is a Client server protocol which uses UDP services. IP address is assigned from a pool of addresses
  
